 Galva flew up towards the blats. He dodged them as his momentium increased. 
He got hit in the shoulder but not much damage was done. The bot wouldnt be 
able to see his movements due to the light the energy was giving off so close 
to him. The bot was shooting still when he stopped about a foot underneath 
the bot he put his hands an inch from the bots stomach he had cupped his 
hands on the way there and when he landed and shot a 20 by 20 foot energy 
blast right through the bots stomach.
